snippet.title: Koolah gameplay (PC Game, 1991)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Koolah, Dos PC game produced by Marko Teittinen in 1991 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/koolah/4122/
Koolah it is an interesting board game, where you try to guide a metal ball through a wooden maze without touching the ball.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
